title: CrimeScene_BrokenVase
---
<<if $crimeScene_vaseExamined == false>>
    <<say cat "This is strange - it seems too far from the rest of the clues, but why?">>
    <<say cat "Was it... thrown?">>
    <<set $crimeScene_vaseExamined = true>>
    <<set $crimeScene_cluesFound += 1>>
    <<if $crimeScene_cluesFound >= 4>>
        <<set $crimeScene_allCluesFound = true>>
    <<endif>>
<<else>>
    <<say cat "The broken vase. Too far from the body to have simply fallen.">>
<<endif>>
===
